      "content": "Please do not change your warfarin dosage without consulting your doctor first, even if you feel fine. Warfarin is a powerful medication, and your current dose is likely calibrated to keep your blood clotting in a safe range for your heart condition. Any sudden change could put you at risk for dangerous clotting or bleeding. Stick to the prescribed regimen and let your healthcare provider manage your anticoagulation therapy.",
